trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> maintains two UserTrackingLocationCollection objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]A<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>维护两个 UserTrackingLocationCollection 对象︰<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>指定用于匹配活动状态事件的参数和<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>指定用于从匹配中排除活动状态事件的参数。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> class.
The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数初始化<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>为空列表。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> class by using a list of user locations.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref>类通过使用用户位置的列表。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects specified in `locations`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>初始化后将包含<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>中指定的对象`locations`。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection>

trans-unit.source: locations is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: locations为空引用 ( 在 Visual Basic 中)。
